 Many women in Oro and Esie Town in Kwara state trooped out to show love and welcome Mercy Aigbe as she visited her husband’s Kazim Adeoti’s hometown. Mercy Aigbe and her husband, Kazim Adeoti had visited lgbomina which happened to be Kazim’s hometown. In the video shared by Mercy Aigbe, many women could be seen giving her a warmly welcome amidst backlash over snatching her friend’s husband. Read Also: I Married Mercy Aigbe To Stop Fornication: Kazim Adeoti Reacting to this video, many of her fans took to the comment section to condemn and praise how the women in Oro Town and Esie Town welcomed Mercy. See reaction below:   